Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia senyum-senyum sendiri\Ntiap 10 detik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia mencoba menutupinya,\Ntapi biarkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, aku tak boleh begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tidak bisa fokus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikiranku melayang terus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami baru pulang berkemah kemarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku baru benar-benar\Nsadar sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira dan aku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berciuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ciuman pertamaku\Ndengan seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, dia menyeringai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya, aku belum pernah pacaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia bakal begini seharian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Dia begitu terus dari pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita pulang sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kita mampir ke bar\Nsetelah makan malam nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa!\NSyukurlah kau bersikap biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, kau sangat tenang,\Ndan itu sangat menarik!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata-katamu agak menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Ma-Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, boleh pinjam tanganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang saat kencan pertama kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak ingin kau berpikir\Ncuma kau yang gugup malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin aku bisa tenang\Ndi bangku perkemahan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kau tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punggung Akira terasa panas sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin\Nkau tidak suka pria seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku suka, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengubah jawabanmu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pesanan Anda, Scarlett O'Hara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gelasnya kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu gelas koktail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pernah ke bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak pernah.\NAku jarang minum di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang pergi ke bar untuk minum, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tempat menikmati alkohol dengan santai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa tempat untuk berduaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyaa! Jantungku berdebar lagi!\NKenapa aku gampang sekali senang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sarankan koktail buah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, langsung kau minum habis.\NKau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau duduk di sana, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan duduk di sisi itu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah pacaran sebelumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:04:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapku selalu kekanak-kanakan!\NKau pasti muak, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, sama sekali tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga lebih tua darimu.\NAku tidak keberatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan perdebatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ciuman itu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah ciuman pertamaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau mau memaafkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Apa aku bersikap\Nkekanak-kanakan lagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh! Aku tak ingin\Nbikin suasana jadi canggung!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak canggung, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Shizuka meminta maaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kencan pertama,\Naku sudah menduga dia belum pernah pacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini, ayo minum air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, minta air putih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira diam sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh! Kenapa aku harus bilang begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kita sudah sampai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Sopir, maukah menunggu\Nbeberapa menit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, apa kau mau mampir minum teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti muak padaku sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, terima kasih banyak\Nsudah mengantarku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari percakapan hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku paham kau punya\Nkekhawatiran tersendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku menunjukkan\Nrasa sayangku padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasih sayangmu sudah lebih dari cukup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baru menaikkan gajiku kemarin lusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.\NAku bisa pulang dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Apa maksudmu, Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fiuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya deras sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sh-Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba hujan deras.\NSeram sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saputanganku sampai basah kuyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah arahkan pemanas ke sofa.\NDuduklah di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini handuk untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau siap sedia sekali.\NApa kau kehujanan juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.\NTak usah pikirkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ugh, kemejaku juga basah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, aku akan mencari selimut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku butuh waktu lama mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanganmu basah dan dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Pakaianmu basah kuyup semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali tidak baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memanfaatkan kebutaanku, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya belum berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemanasnya hangat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menempel padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa berhenti memikirkannya!\NMemalukan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Tangan Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku harus melakukan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat bersamamu seperti ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan ciuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hujannya deras sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kalian kehujanan juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, basah kuyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Kita perlu hangatkan badan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacarmu itu takkan bisa minta sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertemuan pertama kami\Nterasa sangat canggung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya kau harus segera kenalkan Ibu\Nbiar suasananya cair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah ceritanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo. Saya ibunya Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih\Nsudah meluangkan waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.\NMaaf sudah mengganggu tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, saya yang minta maaf\Nkarena tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, terimalah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, roti kacang?\NTerima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kukatakan sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Acara bertemu orang tua begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini saatnya\Nmelamar putri mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih terlalu dini untuk itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Akira berpikir sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu akan sangat membantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Apa yang terjadi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.\NKau tak memperhatikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku meminta penyelidikan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia akan memberiku\Ndiskon calon mertua 30 persen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tujuan Ibu datang ke sini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, jangan mau!\NIbu cuma memanfaatkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian akrab sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu ingin dia menyelidiki apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Mungkin Ayah selingkuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pasang wajah datar begitu, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NKadang ibuku tak tahu malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat gugup setelah insiden\Ndi pertemuan pertama kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sikapnya membuatku\Nmudah bicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau ibu yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harap kau bicara jujur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga membicarakan\Nsesuatu yang penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu yang penting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Shizuka bekerja dengan baik?\NApa dia rukun dengan rekannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hebat dalam pekerjaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang, termasuk saya,\Nbergantung padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah dewasa dan punya pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sangat lega.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, tolong jaga putri saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.\NJangan dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sampai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana kita pergi hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuberi sedikit petunjuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wangi bunga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini bunga mawar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini kita pergi ke taman mawar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dikasih mawar oleh pria?!\NIni pertama kalinya bagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti di novel roman saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanginya luar biasa!\NKita seperti dikelilingi mawar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau yakin\Ntak mau tinggal bunga itu di mobil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku ingin memegangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, aku bertingkah\Nkekanak-kanakan lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, di sini ada kafenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka pakai\Nkelopak mawar untuk kuenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak sekali aroma manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kulihat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scone arah jam 12,\Nsandwich arah jam 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tart arah jam 6,\Ndan keik arah jam 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, dimengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuenya lucu-lucu sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya kue terlihat lucu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuknya mungil,\Nada buah dan krim di atasnya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan warnanya warna-warni, mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mm! Enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggemaskan sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada krim di mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Te-Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ehh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau tipe yang main pukul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, kau mengagetkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang duduk diam\Ndan tunggu seperti anak manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ngapain kau datang hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakan jarak emosional!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Dia punya rencana hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya dia bilang\Nkalau ada rencana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku menganggur\Ndan datang berkunjung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, hadiah teh racikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini hari kerja buat kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, jangan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini-begini,\Naku tak tahan kesepian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, kau lebih galak padaku\Ndibanding ke orang lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo! Ini dari sayangku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai! Ini Dark Elf kesayanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, beri tahu aku sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Light pulang ke rumah keluarganya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami mungkin akan bercerai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takkan terjadi. Mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang peluangnya bukan nol!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya kau pulang\Ndan coba telepon lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mencoba mengusirku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ogah! Tak mau pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibiarkan sendirian,\Naku bisa mati karena cemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah dewasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh dia tinggal sebentar di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku menginap\Ndi tempatmu, Tonome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang! Aku bantu pekerjaan rumah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau serius mau menginap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sudah bangun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau sarapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mandi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong pulang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bikin banyak sup instan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, sudah telepon Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum! Aku terlalu takut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biarkan aku tidur sebentar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat pulang sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya kau agak murung.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terlihat biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan cemas! Kuurus Tonome\Ndengan baik dari ujung kepala sampai kaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sehat dan bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diamlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti bicara ambigu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Tonome,\Nkau benar-benar perusak suasana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak. Aku merasa\Nlebih baik setelah melihat wajahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, hei, hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai ucapan terima kasih\Nboleh menginap kemarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan bantu\Npekerjaan detektifmu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia targetnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mengikutinya.\NSusah kalau dia terbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Takkan selesai kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan ini tak semudah\Nyang kau bayangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu bantu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tak ingin dia terbang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayapku berat...\NKeduanya tak mau bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, kau kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengutuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutukan Dark Elf\Nbisa melemahkan fisik seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi suasana hati kami\Nharus sangat negatif agar berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil banget, tuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku di ambang perceraian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya situasinya\Nlebih parah dari dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, kau boleh menginap\Ndi rumahku malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gantinya, kau harus\Nsegera menelepon istrimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telepon sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini, Tonome,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biarpun tak kasatmata,\Nhawa keberadaanmu kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kubantu tekan nomornya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tak perlu! Aku bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, telepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mereka sudah begini hampir satu jam.\N- Aku akan meneleponnya saat siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin sebenarnya mereka akrab?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Tonome!\NAku pulang hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak tahu, tapi aku lelah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti habis kena badai topan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tidak nyaman\Nberada di dekat Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tidak,\Nsifat kami memang bertolak belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku iri\Nkarena dia sangat terus terang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau coba bersikap terus terang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada orang lain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, cuma kita berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, jangan malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sandaran bahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku terlalu berat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menepuk kepalamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tak kasatmata\Nbiasanya tak begini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ku-Kurasa cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mumpung sedang begini,\Naku ingin meraba wajahmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak keberatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan langka bagiku\Nmeraba wajah orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargamu bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jarang meraba wajah mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan meraba wajahmu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dilihat dari dekat,\Naneh juga kulitmu punya warna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga punya bayangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perubahan warna\Nakibat sirkulasi darah juga menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, tanganmu masuk ke mulutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
